test

Class TestHand

  • java.lang.Object
    • test.TestHand

  • public class TestHand
extends java.lang.Object
    The TestHand class is used by the FiveCardPokerEvalEngineTest as a way to test the getOrderedHand() and handEvaluator() methods in FiveCardPokerEvalEngine. Putting a series of test hands here is a way to keep the code cleaner and easy to read. The TestHand(s) here only have getter methods.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gregory L.Funston
